#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kbookmarkmerger.1.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A program for merging a given set of bookmarks into the user's list of "
"bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Et program som fletter en gitt bokmerkeliste inn i brukerens bokmerkeliste."

